						               													<description>This mini-campaign introduces one of the ways that the real world began to interact with the Black Sun event and allows the players to game out this early period of the Black Sun universe story. This mini-campaign will be set during the early period of the Vietnam War and the first scenario represents a secret operation by CIA agents supported by uniformed US ARMY troops and some local hired labour. The Viet Cong troops are indeed moving through the area and attack this target of opportunity.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Forces are then transported to the BLACK SUN event and all kinds of chaos ensues.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This Operational Campaign is intended for use by new players to the Black Sun universe and introduces background and story elements of horror to the players. This three scenario mini campaign includes new Force Cards for many different factions, new &amp;quot;What the...?!&amp;quot; Cards (ready to print and play) and some new advanced rules including veteran warriors. If you were part of the Black Sun Kickstarter you will have many of the troops needed for this game.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
